---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import elipse from "../assets/img/ellipse-about.svg"
---


    <section class="md:min-h-[936px] grid py-10">
        <div class="max-h-fit">
            <h2 class="text-white font-daciaBold font-bold md:text-4xl text-[2rem] whitespace-pre-line md:leading-[3.5rem]">CONNECTING USERS, SECURING TRADES,
                <span class="text-yellow">GLOBALIZING SPORTSBOOKS</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="md:mt-24 mt-7 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-24">
                <div class="max-w-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-daciaBold font-bold md:text-[1.7rem] text-2xl text-white">
                        OUR MISSION
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white font-inter md:text-base text-sm md:mt-4 mt-2 leading-5 md:leading-6 text-justify">
                        To connect bettors and sportsbooks by offering innovative ways
                        to engage with sports betting, create new revenue streams, and
                        provide decentralized and secure experiences for users and
                        operators worldwide.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="max-w-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-daciaBold font-bold md:text-[1.7rem] text-2xl text-white">
                        OUR VISION
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white font-inter md:text-base text-sm md:mt-4 mt-2 leading-5 md:leading-6 text-justify">
                        To transform gaming for bettors and sportsbooks by building a
                        decentralized global marketplace. Our platform will empower users
                        by providing innovative ways to hedge, sell, and discover bets with
                        greater value, while offering sportsbooks a unique new venue to
                        reach and engage a worldwide audience with exclusive and
                        unconventional betting options through seamlessly integrated
                        technologies on Web3.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <Image src={elipse} alt="elipse" class="absolute -z-50 left-0 top-0" />
    </section>